project.name: SER516 Project 2 Group B Team 4
project.description: This project is for managing the work that Team4 will be doing as part of the Project 2.

content_diff:
* Decided to use Flask based on Python for backend.
* Decided on the API endpoint to be exposed for our first microservice.
* Setting up data for testing for first microservice.
* Decided to generate response in JSON format.
* Will be using ARC for manual testing of the API during the development.
